018}}\n| Director of Operations Chef \n| [[Draper, Virginia]]\n| data-sort-value=\"14\"|[[Hell's Kitchen (American season 14)|Season 14]]\n|rowspan=2|Runner-Up\n| Eliminated after 5th Service\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Kevin Cottle\n| 43{{citation need|date=November 2018}}\n| Executive Chef \n| [[Middletown, Connecticut]]\n| data-sort-value=\"6\"|[[Hell's Kitchen (American season 6)|Season 6]]\n| Eliminated after 4th Service\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | Jennifer \"Jen\" Gavin<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://ediblepassport.com/about-us.html|title=Jennifer Gavin in Asia|date=May 23, 2016|accessdate=December 2, 2018}}</ref>\n| 33{{citation need|date=November 2018}}\n| Private Concert Catering Chef \n| [[Chicago, Illinois]]\n| data-sort-value=\"4\"| [[Hell's Kitchen (American season 4)|Season 4]]\n| 4th\n| Eliminated during 2nd Service\n|}\n\n=== Notes ===\n\n{{reflist|group=n}}\n\n==Contestant progress==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"6\" |\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\" | Original teams\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"7\" | Men and Women Teams\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\" | Switched <br />teams\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\" | Individuals\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\" | Final\n|-\n! No.\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"5\" | Chef\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep267|1801]]/[[#ep268|1802]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep269|1803]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep270|1804]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep271|1805]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep272|1806]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep273|1807]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep274|1808]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep275|1809]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep276|1810]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep277|1811]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep278|1812]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep279|1813]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep280|1814]]/[[#ep281|1815]]\n! scope=\"col\" | [[#ep281|1815]]/[[#ep282|1816]]\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" |'''1'''\n| style=\"background:darkblue |\n| style=\"background:darkblue |\n| style=\"background:darkblue |\n| style=\"background:black |\n| style=\"color:black;\